.TH "LIGHTNING-PEER-DISCONNECT" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-peer-disconnect \- disconnect from a Lightning network peer
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning peer-disconnect
.I pubkey
.SH DESCRIPTION
Disconnects from a Lightning peer identified by its pubkey.
Returns JSON
.B {"ok":true}
on success.
Disconnecting a peer does not close its channels; channels remain
open but temporarily offline until reconnected.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Disconnect request sent.
.TP
.B 5
Disconnect failed.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-peer (1),
.BR lightning-peer-connect (1),
.BR lightning-peer-list (1)
